{"tid":1918225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《有線》記者遭防暴警推跌 林鄭：希望市民諒解包容","createTime":"2020-03-10T03:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T03:39:32.000Z","uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"230156b9f919b80310397a31e81310294490b0a0","tid":1918225,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:11:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200310/_2020031010215967593.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200310%2F_2020031010215967593.jpg&h=70cc644e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線電視一名記者前晚在將軍澳採訪期間，遭一名防暴警用盾牌從後撞跌受傷，警方隨後致函該台致歉。行政長官林鄭月娥表示，非常尊重新聞自由，重視傳媒採訪工作，指警方不可能在電光火石間計劃周詳，希望市民諒解包容。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，過去大半年，現場採訪會出現類似混亂情況，往往是在示威情況，需要警方需進行驅散工作，呼籲按警方指示採訪，保障安全，<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥表示，警方昨已向有線致歉，警隊重視及尊重新聞採訪自由，若記協需與政府和警隊對話，會願意溝通，指警務處處長鄧炳強希望重建警隊與市民的關係，相信警隊會深入了解<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1219099/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A-%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E6%8E%A8%E8%B7%8C-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%AB%92%E8%A7%A3%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1219099%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2581%25AD%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%258E%25A8%25E8%25B7%258C-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E5%25B8%258C%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25AB%2592%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%25AE%25B9&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSnIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=0d51d1c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1219099%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7